# Flutter/Dart/Pub related (monorepo : motifs non ancrés → valables dans chaque package)
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/
.pub/
build/
coverage/
# Lockfiles des packages (seul le lock racine du workspace est versionné)
**/pubspec_overrides.yaml
packages/**/pubspec.lock

# FVM (gestionnaire de versions Flutter)
.fvm/

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here
**/android/app/debug
**/android/app/profile
**/android/app/release

# Widget Preview related
.widget_preview/
